    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mystery adventure where no one dies</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032210/extras/285d4d068a958e99a7ee7153c1e3de42.poster.avif?t=1719279994\" width=416 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032210/extras/285d4d068a958e99a7ee7153c1e3de42.webm?t=1719279994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032210/extras/285d4d068a958e99a7ee7153c1e3de42.mp4?t=1719279994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Detective NEKKO is a cinematic mystery adventure in which the new detective Nekko and partner Zikenbo investigate a case with their &quot;ability to see too much&quot;.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ability ❶ &quot;Seeing the past in your eyes&quot;</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032210/extras/46948d9af21aae1915fdaf30f7625da5.poster.avif?t=1719279994\" width=416 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032210/extras/46948d9af21aae1915fdaf30f7625da5.webm?t=1719279994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032210/extras/46948d9af21aae1915fdaf30f7625da5.mp4?t=1719279994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The main focus of this work is the investigation of the suspect's alibi<br>The investigation is conducted in the past on the day of the incident, experienced from the suspect's first-person point of view.<br>Find the contradiction between the lies told by the suspect's mouth and the truth told by his eyes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ability ➋ &quot;bird's eye view&quot;</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032210/extras/f477d1575931145d920a69f71d917c37.poster.avif?t=1719279994\" width=416 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032210/extras/f477d1575931145d920a69f71d917c37.webm?t=1719279994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032210/extras/f477d1575931145d920a69f71d917c37.mp4?t=1719279994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The entire case as revealed by the alibi investigation is reviewed and organized.<br>By comparing the actions of all the suspects, the frayed edges of testimony will be revealed.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ability ➌ &quot;Seeing trust&quot;</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032210/extras/23c6318fc6eb8f3cc33b4aab9cdfb64c.poster.avif?t=1719279994\" width=416 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032210/extras/23c6318fc6eb8f3cc33b4aab9cdfb64c.webm?t=1719279994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032210/extras/23c6318fc6eb8f3cc33b4aab9cdfb64c.mp4?t=1719279994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>It shows how much they trust us.<br>How you think as a detective and how you respond.<br>Trust fluctuates slightly, and the end result of the story can be very different.",
